description: Lists the mobile device access rules for the specified WorkMail organization.

parameters.name: OrganizationId
parameters.description: The WorkMail organization for which to list the rules.

nested_items.name: Rules
nested_items.description: The list of mobile device access rules that exist under the specified WorkMail organization.

nested_items.name: MobileDeviceAccessRuleId
nested_items.description: The ID assigned to a mobile access rule.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of a mobile access rule.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The description of a mobile access rule.

nested_items.name: Effect
nested_items.description: The effect of the rule when it matches. Allowed values are ALLOW or DENY.

nested_items.name: DeviceTypes
nested_items.description: Device types that a rule will match.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: NotDeviceTypes
nested_items.description: Device types that a rule will not match. All other device types will match.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: DeviceModels
nested_items.description: Device models that a rule will match.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: NotDeviceModels
nested_items.description: Device models that a rule will not match. All other device models will match.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: DeviceOperatingSystems
nested_items.description: Device operating systems that a rule will match.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: NotDeviceOperatingSystems
nested_items.description: Device operating systems that a rule will not match. All other device types will match.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: DeviceUserAgents
nested_items.description: Device user agents that a rule will match.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: NotDeviceUserAgents
nested_items.description: Device user agents that a rule will not match. All other device user agents will match.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: DateCreated
nested_items.description: The date and time at which an access rule was created.

nested_items.name: DateModified
nested_items.description: The date and time at which an access rule was modified.
